repo.name: Huizengek's apps/forks
repo.description: This is a repository of apps to be used with F-Droid. Applications in this repository are binaries buit from source by Huizengek using the toold on https://gitlab.com/fdroid

en-US.description:
An ad-free WhatsApp sticker maker.

* Create stickers of images or text and import them in WhatsApp.
en-US.name: snpack
en-US.whatsNew:
* Changed placeholders to more generic ones
* Added English translations
* Added predictive back animation
* Fixed UI inconsistencies

nl-NL.description:
Een advertentievrije WhatsApp sticker maker.

* Maak stickers van afbeeldingen of tekst en importeer ze in WhatsApp.
nl-NL.name: snpack
nl-NL.summary: Een Nederlandse, advertentievrije WhatsApp sticker maker.
nl-NL.whatsNew:
* Placeholders veranderd naar meer generieke placeholders
* Support voor voorspelbare terug-animaties toegevoegd
* Engelse vertalingen toegevoegd
* UI inconsistenties gefixt

en-US.description: Features: * Search and play any song or video from YouTube Music * Background playback w/ notification * Search for songs, albums, artists, videos and playlists * Discover new songs by mood/genre * Bookmark artists and albums * Import playlists * Import local music * Share to import from other YouTube Music apps * Automatic cache system for offline playback and saving resources * Fetch and edit lyrics and synchronized lyrics * Open YouTube/YouTube Music links * Local playlists management * Queue management * Favorites and Offline built-in playlists * Sleep timer * Skip silence * Persistent queue * Loudness/audio normalization * Android Auto * Simple and minimal UI * Ridiculously lightweight APK
en-US.name: ViMusic
en-US.summary: Seamlessly stream music from YouTube Music
en-US.whatsNew:
* Optimized performance
* Fixed edge cases that caused the duration of a song to appear incorrectly
* Fixed an issue that caused ghost files to appear in Local music in some cases
* Fixed an edge case that caused the app to crash when non-synchronized lyrics are enabled
* Move to adminforge.de as the main Piped instance to bypass some restrictions and avoid downtime
* Fixed slider behavior
* Fixed an issue that caused the app to crash when your device is out of memory or doesn't support normaliz
